Index: https://ilyadev.xyz/llms-ru.txt — full case-study list
Author: Demo Author — https://ilyadev.xyz/index.ru.txt
"
`;

exports[`caseStudyToMarkdown — snapshots > RU · macos-vpn 1`] = `
"# macOS Network Guard · Demo client

\`05 · macos-vpn · Demo\`

Вымышленный macOS menu-bar client: per-app network policy, connection state и kill-switch behavior без private infrastructure details.

**Scope:** Demo · desktop systems  
**Role:** Desktop network-control demo с explicit failure states

---

## Контекст

> Network tools fail. Product должен показать which state failed.

Вымышленный client сфокусирован на user-facing стороне network-control product: state clarity, predictable app policy и failure modes, которые не expose traffic silently.

Private endpoints, keys и provider details намеренно отсутствуют. Public case оставляет system shape: menu-bar surface, connection state machine, policy storage и guardrails вокруг unsafe transitions.

## Факты

| | |
|---|---|
| **Surface** | macOS menu-bar utility |
| **Policy** | Per-app allow/block routing model |
| **State** | Disconnected · connecting · protected · degraded · blocked |
| **Safety** | Kill-switch state visible, not silent |

## Архитектура

### Connection state model

\`\`\`text
connect -> connecting -> protected
   |            | error        | tunnel lost
   v            v              v
blocked <- degraded <- reconnect attempt
\`\`\`

**Blocked.** Unsafe traffic остаётся blocked до user или policy exit.

**UI.** Каждый state maps to one visible label and one allowed action set.

## Ключевые инженерные решения

### 01 · State machine before UI polish

**Решение.** Connection state modeled as explicit states with allowed transitions.

**Почему.** Network products fail в edges; implicit booleans hide those edges.

**Цена.** Больше upfront modeling до finished-looking UI.

### 02 · Policy is separate from session

**Решение.** Per-app routing policy хранится отдельно от active connection session.

**Почему.** User должен менять policy без accidental mutation current tunnel state.

**Цена.** UI должен clearly explain pending vs active policy.

### 03 · Unsafe state stays visible

**Решение.** Kill-switch activation показывается как first-class blocked state.

**Почему.** Security feature, которая hides itself, создаёт support debt и confusion.

**Цена.** Больше copy и edge-case handling в menu-bar surface.

## Стек

| | |
|---|---|
| **App** | SwiftUI-style menu-bar surface |
| **Network** | NetworkExtension concepts · guarded tunnel state |
| **Policy** | Per-app routing table · persisted preferences |
| **Helper** | Signed helper model · privileged boundary notes |
| **Testing** | State transition fixtures · disconnect scenarios |
| **Privacy** | No private endpoints, keys, or real client media |

## Уроки и статус

### Оставлю как есть

- Explicit states лучше boolean connection flags.
- Policy editing нужен отдельный mental model от active sessions.
- Unsafe network behavior должен быть visible.

### Поменял бы

- Model degraded mode до icon design.
- Provider-specific logic держать за narrow adapter.
- Failure copy писать вместе со state machine.

Fictionalized desktop case для public repo review.

---

Source: https://ilyadev.xyz/cases/macos-vpn (HTML) · /cases/macos-vpn.ru.txt (this file)
