Index: https://ilyadev.xyz/llms-ru.txt — full case-study list
Author: Demo Author — https://ilyadev.xyz/index.ru.txt
"
`;

exports[`caseStudyToMarkdown — snapshots > RU · portfolio-site 1`] = `
"# Portfolio Engine · Public repo case

\`06 · portfolio-site · Open engine\`

Реальный architecture case для этого repo: typed bilingual content, route-aware case pages, text mirrors for agents и privacy-first analytics.

**Scope:** Production engine · public demo content  
**Role:** Frontend architecture, content system, telemetry и static publishing

---

## Контекст

> Portfolio как resume слабее. Portfolio как auditable system сильнее.

Проект начался как portfolio page и стал small publishing engine. Это intentional: site одновременно resume surface и proof artifact, который другой engineer может clone, inspect и reason about.

Public version commits sanitized demo content by default. Private content и private media живут в ignored trees, selected only by explicit public/private scripts that generate the active barrel before dev, typecheck and build.

## Факты

| | |
|---|---|
| **Content** | Typed EN/RU/AR structures, not string-key resources |
| **Publishing** | SPA routes plus generated per-case static heads |
| **Agents** | Text mirrors and llms.txt generated at build time |
| **Telemetry** | Same-origin endpoint, no third-party tracker |

## Архитектура

### Public/private content selection

\`\`\`text
npm script -> CONTENT_SOURCE -> select-content.mjs
                         | public/private |
                         v                v
              public demo exports      .private exports
                         \\              /
                          src/content/active.ts
\`\`\`

**Default.** Plain dev/build fail until public или private script chosen.

**Private.** Local ignored tree overrides copy and media only through explicit private scripts.

### Build outputs

\`\`\`text
typed content -> React UI
             -> public/dev mirrors or private dist mirrors
             -> llms.txt + per-page text mirrors
             -> dist/cases/<slug>/index.html with case head
\`\`\`

**Humans.** SPA stays fast and route-aware.

**Agents.** Text mirrors expose same case structure without UI scraping.

## Ключевые инженерные решения

### 01 · Typed content over i18n runtime

**Решение.** Site keeps custom typed content object вместо i18next.

**Почему.** Project needs structure, autocomplete and compile-time locale parity more than plural rules or translation-management workflows.

**Цена.** Third locale later means another typed content tree.

### 02 · Generated active barrel

**Решение.** Explicit public/private scripts write src/content/active.ts pointing at selected content tree.

**Почему.** TypeScript, Vite config and build-time generators see one import path without runtime alias tricks.

**Цена.** Generated file must stay gitignored and created before typecheck/build; plain build/dev intentionally fail instead of guessing.

### 03 · Static head copies for case routes

**Решение.** Build writes dist/cases/<slug>/index.html with case-specific title, description, alternate text links and JSON-LD.

**Почему.** Social scrapers and many bots do not run client JavaScript; client-only head updates are insufficient.

**Цена.** Small Vite plugin owns index.html injection.

## Стек

| | |
|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React · TypeScript · Vite 7 |
| **Design** | CSS custom properties · route-aware case styling |
| **Content** | Generated active barrel · public/private trees |
| **Agents** | Text mirrors · llms.txt · per-case alternates |
| **Analytics** | Node ingest · SQLite · same-origin proxy |
| **CI** | Lint · unit tests · typecheck · build · audit · leakage guards |

## Уроки и статус

### Оставлю как есть

- Portfolio can be proof artifact, not only brochure.
- Typed content gives better refactor safety than string keys here.
- Agent-readable mirrors make work inspectable without UI scraping.
- Pure helpers exported from both modules become natural test surface — Markdown serializers, payload validators, dwell classifier.

### Поменял бы

- Sanitization must include media, not only text.
- Static metadata should be generated before publication.
- CI should guard leakage patterns from first public push.
- Public proof needs executable checks around mirrors, telemetry validation, and content parity — type signatures alone do not catch array-length drift between EN and RU trees.

Real architecture case with sanitized author-facing copy.

---

Source: https://ilyadev.xyz/cases/portfolio-site (HTML) · /cases/portfolio-site.ru.txt (this file)
